quran[29]{c,v,t,f}:
  77,49,"Ipotesi lyele lisikulyo taachiipata ŵakanila."
  77,50,"Ana ni abalichi jatachijikulupilila panyuma pa aji (Qur’an)?"
  79,40,"Sano jwaakogopa kuti tachija kwima pameso pa Ambujegwe (Allah), nikuwukanyaga ntima ku isako yakusakala."
  79,41,"Chisimu Litimbe lya ku Mbepo basi ni liuto lyakwe."
  79,42,"Akum'buusya (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ya ndema (jakwichila Kiyama kuti): “Jichiŵa chakachi?”"
  80,37,"Mundu jwalijose mwa ŵanganyao lyele lisikulyo tachikola yakunkwanila (kuntendekasya kuti akakosoŵalila ya jwine.)"
  80,38,"Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa syakumelemenda."
  80,39,"Syakusechelela ni kusengwa (pakupikana yakuja ku Mbepo)."
  83,25,"Takamwesyedweje nkologo wambone nnope wesiŵe (ni isiŵilo yakulimbangana)."
  83,26,"Kumbesi kwa kumwako (chikukanunjileje luwumba lwa) miski. Sano kuti akaipate yele basi apikisane akupikisana (pakutenda yambone)."
  83,27,"Soni chakuwanganyichisya chakwe (nkologowo chigakaŵe) mesi gakuumila mu Tasnim."
  84,22,"Nambo kuti achimakafili agamba kanila basi."
  84,23,"Sano Allah ni jwaakuyimanya chenene yaakusonganganya ŵanganyao."
  84,24,"Basi mwatagulilani ya ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope."
  85,19,"Nambo kuti achimakafili ali mu kukanila basi."
  85,20,"Sano Allah ni ŵasyungulile chakunyuma kwao."
  85,21,"Nambo jalakweji ni Qur’an Jakuchimbichika."
  86,13,"Chisimu jalakwe (Qur’aniji) gaŵele maloŵe gakulekanganya (chilikati cha yakuona ni yaunami)."
  86,14,"Soni jalakweji nganijiŵa chindu chambenje."
  86,15,"Chisimu ŵanganyao akuŵa ali nkutenda malindi (kwa Asilamu)."
  87,10,"Talikumbusye mundu jwaakun'jogopa (Allah)."
  87,11,"Ni takuŵambale (mundu) jwakusakala nnope."
  87,12,"Ajula jwatakajinjile ku Moto Wekulungwa."
  88,7,"Jangajimbasya soni jangakamuchisya ku sala."
  88,8,"Ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichiŵa m’chindimba."
  88,9,"Ligongo lya masengo gakwe (gambone) sichiŵa syakusengwa."
  89,4,"Ni chilo ndema jachikuŵigula."
  89,5,"Ana mu yalakweyi ngaŵa mwana kulumbila kwakwanila, kwa jwakwete lunda?"
  89,6,"Ana nganinyyiona yaŵatite Ambuje ŵenu kaape ipotesi ŵanya Adi?"